snippet.title: Linkin Park Medal of Honor Warfighter Trailer - E3 2012 Multiplayer Gameplay
snippet.description:
http://www.medalofhonor.com/watch
The Official Medal of Honor E3 Multiplayer Gameplay trailer.  Watch as US SFOD-D, NAVY SEALs, US OGA, Polish GROM, Australian SASR and Canadian JTF2 compete for title of best of the best. Featuring "LIES GREED MISERY " From Linkin Park's upcoming Album "LIVING THINGS". Pre-Order the Album now at http://smarturl.it/LIVINGTHINGS.

Powered by the Frostbite 2 Engine.

For more information about the Global Operators and the Most Authentic Shooter to date, go to http://www.medalofhonor.com/

Strike First on Oct. 23th, 2012 for the PlayStation3, Xbox 360 and PC
